    {
      "label": "Content description",
      "value": "Recto: Individual\u2019s list of payments. The records of payments are followed by the total of an outstanding debt.\nVerso: This letter, in an unpractised hand, has been written to the mother of the sender (l. 6). The letter starts with familiar opening greetings and the announcement that the sender\u2019s family is in good health. The sender refers to a letter from the addressee (ll. 5-8). The request by a third person to the addressee to buy some goods is passed on in this letter (ll. 12-15)."
    },
